title: Risk Scores
description: Risk scoring (0–100) for routing, escalation, and reporting.
---

> **Version:** v1.1.0  
> This page documents behavior guaranteed in TealTiger v1.1.0.


# Risk Scores

## Contract

- `risk_score` is a number from 0 to 100 (inclusive)
- Higher score indicates higher risk

## Recommended usage

- >= 80: escalate / approval
- 50–79: warn / extra logging
- < 50: proceed
